      <h2 class="post"><a href="/2013/04/26/configstore-debug-sublime">Yeoman Configstore, Debug.js, Sublime JavaScript Refactoring</a></h2>

<div class="meta">
  26 Apr 2013 |
  <span class="author">By Alex Young</span> |
  <span class="tags">
    <img alt="Tags" class="icon" src="/images/tag.gif" />
    
